remote_controller protocol

<sep> - separator, is declarate by user(different from ',')
ID - is unique identificator every Component, set by user
METHOD ID - is unique identificator every Method in every type of Component
arg1, arg2, ... - user data input field, every method can have different number of arguments


Example request:
ID<sep>METHOD ID<sep>arg1,arg2,arg3<sep><sep>

On end the request is double <sep>



How control android Component (INPUT COMPONENT)?

LED
ID<sep>"toggle"<sep><sep>
ID<sep>"off"<sep><sep>
ID<sep>"on"<sep><sep>

TextArea
ID<sep>"clear"<sep><sep>
ID<sep>"write"<sep>arg1<sep><sep>
ID<sep>"append"<sep>arg1<sep><sep>




What data is return by android Compontent (OUTPUT COMPONENT)?
BUTTON
onClick - return data from onClickField, which is set by user
